        <p>Material covered: some properties of composition of linear maps (products), and an introduction to kernels and images (or nullspaces and ranges).</p>
<div class="toc">
<ul>
<li><a href="#composition-of-linear-maps-properties">1 Composition of linear maps: properties</a></li>
<li><a href="#kernels-and-images">2 Kernels and images</a><ul>
<li><a href="#kernels">2.1 Kernels</a><ul>
<li><a href="#relation-to-injectivity">2.1.1 Relation to injectivity</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="#images">2.2 Images</a></li>
